snippet.title: Raging Bytes - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Raging Bytes is a story-driven pixel-art mobile zombie RPG set in a fictional 1970s post-apocalyptic United States. The game comes packed with a turn-based combat system full of depth, difficulty levels for all kinds of players, and plenty of supplies to scavenge for your survival. Raging Bytes is available now on iOS and Android.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
